CREATE TABLE TB_OUT_HEADER
( 
	DAT			VARCHAR2(8) NOT NULL,
	OUT_NUM		NUMBER      NOT NULL,
	DEPT					VARCHAR2(30),
	REASON					VARCHAR2(30),
	FOR_COMPANY				VARCHAR2(200),
	STATUS					VARCHAR2(50),
	IN_ID					VARCHAR2(10),
	IN_DATE					DATE,
	ACC_FLAG				VARCHAR2(1 CHAR),
	ACC_ID					VARCHAR2(10),
	RENEW_DATE				DATE,
	RENEW_ID				CHAR(10),
	VENDOR_ID				VARCHAR2(20),
	REMARK_MAIN				VARCHAR2(50),
	ACC_MODEL				VARCHAR2(100),
	ACC_SYMBOL				VARCHAR2(100),
	ACC_NUMBER				VARCHAR2(30),
	ACC_DATE				DATE,
	PRINT_FLAG				VARCHAR2(1 CHAR),
	NUMBER_CAR				VARCHAR2(30),
	NUMBER_CONTRACT			VARCHAR2(30)
);

CREATE TABLE TB_OUT_N_DETAIL
( 
	OUT_LINE_NUM		NUMBER NOT NULL,
	OUT_NUM				NUMBER NOT NULL,
	OUT_NUM_DETAIL		NUMBER NOT NULL,
	ITEM_CODE					VARCHAR2(100),
	DESCRIPTION					VARCHAR2(500),
	UOM							VARCHAR2(10),
	QTY							NUMBER,
	EXCHANGE					VARCHAR2(50),
	REMAR						VARCHAR2(200),
	IN_ID						VARCHAR2(10),
	IN_DATE						DATE,
	PROG_ID						VARCHAR2(10),
	RETURN_QTY					NUMBER,
	RETURN_ID					VARCHAR2(10),
	RETURN_DATE					DATE,
	RENEW_ID					VARCHAR2(10),
	RENEW_DATE					DATE,
	ACC_FLAG					VARCHAR2(1 CHAR),
	ACC_ID						VARCHAR2(10)

);

SELECT
    a.dat,
    a.out_num,
    'CONG TY TNHH VIEÄT NAM SAMHO' AS xuat_kho,
    a.reason,
    a.for_company,
    a.number_car,
    a.number_contract,
    b.remar,
    b.uom,
    a.acc_flag,
    a.print_flag,
    SUM(b.qty) AS qty
FROM
    mes.tb_out_header     a,
    mes.tb_out_n_detail   b
WHERE
    a.out_num = b.out_num
    AND a.acc_flag = 'Y'
    AND a.print_flag = 'Y'
    AND a.acc_model IS NULL
    AND a.acc_symbol IS NULL
    AND a.acc_number IS NULL
    AND a.acc_date IS NULL
    AND a.out_num <= ?
GROUP BY
    a.dat,
    a.out_num,
    a.reason,
    a.for_company,
    a.number_car,
    a.number_contract,
    b.remar,
    b.uom,
    a.acc_flag,
    a.print_flag
